      "blocks": {
        "text_review_ELAGqe": {
          "type": "text_review",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/1766070306__1766070305474-celeste__huge.jpg",
            "review_title": "\"My fiancée is over the moon with her ring!\"",
            "review_text": "<p>Cannot thank the team at Griffin & Co enough, they helped me design the most beautiful bespoke engagement ring for my fiancée!</p><p>They made the whole process so enjoyable and unique to me.</p>",
            "author": "Celeste",
            "verified": true,
            "verified_color": "#004225",
            "date": "18-12-2025"
          }
        },
        "text_review_yzViaz": {
          "type": "text_review",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/1768495195__1768495191976-unnamed__huge.jpg",
            "review_title": "\"I couldn’t be happier with my experience.\"",
            "review_text": "<p>Cian and the whole team were fantastic from start to finish. We were never rushed and were given plenty of time to consider our options. </p><p>After some thought, we asked Cian to design a ring for us, and the result is absolutely amazing. Would highly recommend</p>",
            "author": "Bobby",
            "verified": true,
            "verified_color": "#004225",
            "date": "9-1-2026"
          }
        },
        "text_review_6UhwaK": {
          "type": "text_review",
          "settings": {
            "review_title": "\"Lovely shopping experience today.\"",
            "review_text": "<p>Great service and very happy with purchase. Would recommend.</p>",
            "author": "Kevin",
            "verified": true,
            "verified_color": "#004225",
            "date": "10-04-2026"
          }
        },
        "text_review_KLTMhJ": {
          "type": "text_review",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/1766070332__1766070330520-mcmatt__huge.jpg",
            "review_title": "\"Purchased a bracelet from Griffin & Co. as a gift, great quality and looks amazing\"",
            "review_text": "<p>Cannot thank the team at Griffin & Co enough, they helped me design the most beautiful bespoke engagement ring for my fiancée!</p><p>They made the whole process so enjoyable and unique to me.</p>",
            "author": "McMatt",
            "verified": true,
            "verified_color": "#004225",
            "date": "15-12-2025"
          }
        },
        "text_review_qfgQib": {
          "type": "text_review",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/1766070257__1766070251766-lauren__original_668a97dc-9b6b-417f-b31c-caa0a77114b6.avif",
            "review_title": "\"I returned to Griffin after having such a wonderful experience previously, and once again they truly exceeded my expectations.\"",
            "review_text": "<p>This time, I brought in some very sentimental pieces of jewellery to be remodelled, and the team couldn’t have been more attentive and professional. </p><p>They took the time to listen carefully to my ideas, offered helpful guidance, and perfectly brought my design to life. The finished piece is absolutely stunning and holds so much meaning to me. I wouldn’t hesitate to recommend them to anyone looking for exceptional service and craftsmanship.</p>",
            "author": "Lauren",
            "verified": true,
            "verified_color": "#004225",
            "date": "29-9-2025"
          }
        },
        "text_review_mpdipj": {
